OL,6,FMark Walker, Interim Service Director
OL,7,Ffor Place at Nottinghamshire County
OL,8,FCouncil, said: "I'd like to thank and
OL,9,Frecognise all of the victims who came
OL,10,Fforward and worked with our
OL,11,Finvestigators to bring this case to
OL,12,Ftrial and these individuals to justice.
OL,14,F"These sentences show that the
OL,15,Fdishonest selling of products will not
OL,16,Fbe tolerated.
OL,18,F"There is a saying that if something
OL,19,Fseems too good to be true, then it
OL,20,Fprobably is and sadly scammers hope to
OL,21,Fexploit this for their own gain.
