OL,6,F"We would always advise residents to
OL,7,Fbe alert to cold calling and to never
OL,8,Fbuy at the door. If residents have any
OL,9,Fconcerns or if something doesn't feel
OL,10,Fright, then it probably isn't, and
OL,11,Fnobody should ever be afraid to close
OL,12,Fthe door.
OL,14,F"Scammers may turn up out of the blue
OL,15,Foffering something you didn't think
OL,16,Fthat you needed, but by working
OL,17,Ftogether to spot their behaviour we
OL,18,Fcan make sure that they don't take
OL,19,Fadvantage of friends, loved ones and
OL,20,Fneighbours.
